<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <style>
      .imgLogo {
        width: 72px;
        height: 72px;
        margin-right: 14px;
      }
      .titleName {
        color: rgb(53, 137, 234);
        font-size: 31px;
        line-height: 29px;
        font-family: Arial;
      }
      .container {
        padding: 20px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        .main {
          flex: 1;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class="container">
    <header>
      <div style="display: flex">
        <div>
          <img
            class="imgLogo"
            src="https://d2g5hra3l2p3a0.cloudfront.net/files/avatar/64a24916bda5b01a61ce552c/logo.png"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="titleName">IoT Platform</div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main">
      <div class="title">
        <p>Dear Mr./Mrs./Ms. <%= firstName %>,</p>
        <div></div>

        <p>
          We are writing to notify you that your account status has been updated
          from active to inactive. This alteration could impact your access to
          specific features or functionalities within our system.
        </p>
        <div></div>

        <p>
          If you have any inquiries or concerns regarding this adjustment or
          wish to reactivate your account, please feel free to reach out to our
          customer support team at
          <a href="mailto:<%= emailSupport %>"> <%= emailSupport %> </a>. We
          apologize for any inconvenience this may cause and appreciate your
          understanding.
        </p>
        <div></div>

        <p>
          If you have any further questions or concerns, please do not hesitate
          to contact our customer support team.
        </p>
        <div></div>

        <p>Sincerely,</p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
